casebody.data:
Benno M. BRINK, Trustee in Bankruptcy of The BREAKFAST CLUB, Inc., Bankrupt, Appellant, v. COLLECTOR OF INTERNAL REVENUE, Appellee. No. 8040. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Nov. 25, 1935. Paul W. Sampsell, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellant. Peirson M. Hall, U. S. Atty., of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellee.

Before WILBUR, GARRECHT, and DENMAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
